 XP PRACTICES (Technical + Example)

 ğŸŸ¦ 1. Pair Programming

 Technical

Two developers work on one system.

 One writes code
 One reviews

Reduces bugs.

---

 ğŸ‘©â€â¤ï¸â€ğŸ‘¨ Example

Husband cooking.
Wife watching:

> Add salt carefully.

Mistakes avoided.

---

 ğŸ¢ IT example

Banking payment module.
Two developers code together to avoid errors.

---

 ğŸŸ¦ 2. Test Driven Development (TDD)

 Technical

Write test case first.
Then write code.

Ensures correct logic.

---

 ğŸ‘©â€â¤ï¸â€ğŸ‘¨ Example

Wife reads recipe fully
then starts cooking.

